  "form": "任意団体 internal press + publishing + translation substrate (NOT 一般社団 / NPO / 公益財団 / 宗教法人 法人格; NOT a state-licensed press entity — Preamble §0.4 Lv7+ unanimity lock)",
  "culturalLineage": "古代日本 語部 class (oral historian); 万人祭司 priesthood of all believers (Charter §1.7); Sola Scriptura (scripture-access-through-translation); Charter §1.7 多世代 chronicle preservation; Charter §1.15 non-eschatological tone",
